    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis retains its signature balance thanks to aluminum lower control arms and a front strut tower brace, ensuring neutral handling and precise feedback. A mechanically honest example optimized for the driving enthusiast.",
