    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available now is a beautifully maintained 2017 Porsche Macan S finished in Rhodium Silver Metallic with a refined Black leather interior. This vehicle has been treated with care and serves as a perfect example of a daily-driver-ready performance SUV. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, though close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather seats are supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and the dashboard remains free of any cracks or sun damage. All interior technology, including the PCM navigation system, heated seats, and the panoramic glass roof, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this Macan S is in excellent health. It features a documented service history, including a recent major service involving new spark plugs and a fresh oil change. The turbocharged V6 delivers power smoothly, and the PDK transmission shifts with crisp precision. The tires are matching Pirellis with ample tread remaining. This is a complete package for the discerning buyer who values mechanical integrity and a clean aesthetic. Sale includes two keys, floor mats, and a folder of recent maintenance receipts.",
