    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, offering direct engagement and precise shift gates. The chassis has been addressed with essential subframe reinforcement, mitigating the common floor-pan fatigue issues associated with this platform. Performance is anchored by a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. Recent technical overhead includes a comprehensive valve shim adjustment and a cooling system refresh with a high-flow water pump. While the aesthetics show the honest patina of a driven machine, the powertrain remains tight, delivering a linear power band and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. This is an analog driver's car optimized for longitudinal and lateral dynamics.",
